{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":true,"promptId":"dab2980e-33bb-43b0-8f99-a0f5746d8221","agentId":"a8cea69907ce3b021","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"You are an implementer. Fix 3 quality issues in `/Users/xpeng/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/agents/legacy-translator.md`.\n\n## Issue 1 (Critical): OC method name grep pattern is wrong\n\nCurrent function grep pattern (find this block):\n```bash\ngrep -rn \"func <target>\\|-(void)<target>\\|- (<target>\\|void <target>(\" <project_root> \\\n  --include=\"*.swift\" --include=\"*.m\" --include=\"*.cpp\" \\\n  2>/dev/null | grep -v Pods | grep -v DerivedData | head -5\n```\n\nThe pattern `- (<target>` incorrectly matches return type, not method name. Fix by replacing `- (<target>` with `)[ ]*<target>` to correctly match OC method names after the closing paren of the return type.\n\nReplace with:\n```bash\ngrep -rn \"func <target>\\|-(void)<target>\\|)[ ]*<target>\\|void <target>(\" <project_root> \\\n  --include=\"*.swift\" --include=\"*.m\" --include=\"*.cpp\" \\\n  2>/dev/null | grep -v Pods | grep -v DerivedData | head -5\n```\n\n## Issue 2 (Yellow): `ClassName.method` format (contains `.`) misrouted as file path\n\nThe file path detection condition is \"包含 `/` 或 `.`\" which would misroute `AudioEngine.init` to the file path branch.\n\nFind this text:\n```\n**文件路径**（包含 `/` 或 `.`）：\n```\n\nReplace with:\n```\n**文件路径**（包含 `/`，或包含 `.` 但不含 `#pragma`；注意：形如 `ClassName.method` 的复合函数名以函数名分支处理，不走此分支）：\n```\n\n## Issue 3 (Yellow): OC pragma branch missing grep command\n\nThe OC pragma section says \"Grep 定位包含该 section 的文件\" but gives no command. Find this block:\n\n```\n**OC pragma 块**（包含 `#pragma mark`）：\n- 从 `target` 中提取 section 名称（`#pragma mark - ` 后的部分）\n- Grep 定位包含该 section 的文件，读取该 `#pragma mark` 段落内的所有方法\n```\n\nReplace with:\n```\n**OC pragma 块**（包含 `#pragma mark`）：\n- 从 `target` 中提取 section 名称（`#pragma mark - ` 后的部分，记为 `<section>`）\n- 使用以下命令定位文件：\n```bash\ngrep -rl \"#pragma mark.*<section>\" <project_root> \\\n  --include=\"*.m\" --include=\"*.h\" \\\n  2>/dev/null | grep -v Pods | grep -v DerivedData | head -3\n```\n- 读取找到的文件，提取该 `#pragma mark - <section>` 至下一个 `#pragma mark` 之间的所有方法\n```\n\n## Steps\n\n1. Read the file at `/Users/xpeng/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/agents/legacy-translator.md`\n2. Apply the 3 edits above using the Edit tool\n3. Run: `cd /Users/xpeng/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader && git add agents/legacy-translator.md && git commit -m \"fix(legacy-translator): fix OC method grep pattern, compound function name routing, pragma grep\"`\n4. Report DONE"},"uuid":"ee58a3eb-10ad-46f9-8b14-5d7d17b0f057","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:15:51.715Z","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/xpeng/Desktop/AiStudy/claude-learn/plugin-dev","sessionId":"95b3d4f4-8123-4885-9752-f1e600f4a1f6","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"frolicking-honking-lake"}
